Package org.diachron.detection.utils

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ChangesDetector
    This class is responsible for the change detection between two named graph versions.
    ChangesManager
    Similar to DatasetsManager where a dataset URI is connected with its versions, in this class we have a dataset changes URI which is connected with its changes ontologies.
    DatasetsManager
    This class is responsible for the management of various dataset versions which refer on a specific dataset URI.
    IOOps  
    JSONMessagesParser
    This class contains a set of static methods which are used for the definition of a complex change using a JSON string as input.
    MCDUtils  
    SCDUtils
    This class contains methods which refer on a change detection of a specific versions pair.
